          "values": [
            {
              "mapValue": {
                "fields": {
                  "content": {
                    "stringValue": "I'm in meetings all day and honestly, [Otter.ai](https://otter.ai/) saved my sanity. I used to scramble taking notes, but now I just let it listen and it catches things I totally missed. If you're drowning in Zoom calls, it's a total game changer."
