                  "content": {
                    "stringValue": "I found this tool called [Runway](https://runwayml.com/) for video stuff. I'm not a pro editor, but being able to just type what I want to change in a video is wild. It's like having a Hollywood studio in my browser. Definitely check out their Generative Fill feature."
