                  "content": {
                    "stringValue": "I usually think most AI is overhyped, but [Perplexity](https://www.perplexity.ai/) actually won me over. It's basically what Google used to be before all the ads. It gives you direct answers with sources so you can actually verify stuff. It's the only AI app I use daily now."
